\par }\pard \qj \fi170\li0\ri0\sl264\slmult1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cgrid0 Still, observations are a powerful tool, if properly used. People who suffer from personality disorders have many things in common:}{
\par }\pard \qj \fi-142\li312\ri0\sl264\slmult1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin312\itap0 {\bullet \tab 
