nd privileged basis. They complain about numerous symptoms. They never obey the physician or his treatment recommendations and instructions.
\par }{\cgrid0 \bullet \tab They regard themselves as unique, display a streak of grandiosity and a diminished capacity for empathy (the abil
ity to appreciate and respect the needs and wishes of other people). They regard the physician as inferior to them, alienate him using umpteen techniques and bore him with their never-ending self-preoccupation.}{
