ght disorders (except those who suffer from the Borderline Personality Disorder and who experience brief psychotic "microepisodes", mostly during treatment).}{
\par }\pard \qj \fi170\li0\ri0\sl264\slmult1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cgrid0 They are also fully oriented, with clear senses (sensorium), good memory and general fund of knowl
