\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl264\slmult1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\i Answer:}{ Many of my correspondents complain of the incredible deceptive powers of the narcissist. They found themselves involved with narc
